data.description: Looking for privacy? Come see this secluded countryside retreat on 10.26 acres. Move-in ready condition. Open floor plan with main level living plus walkout basement.  Approximately 2,100 sq. ft. of total living area.  Split bedroom floor plan each with it's own bath.  Gorgeous 5" hickory floors, pine tongue and groove ceiling, custom cabinetry with soft close features.  The exterior features low maintenance Hardiplank siding, composite decking on 12x8 front porch and double car side-loading attached garage. This property is surrounded by woods and farmland yet minutes from Rt. 262 offering convenience for commuters in all directions!
